Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:14.15,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,950)\pos(140,435)\fsp5\blur2}红的极秘任务\N与第三代的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次任務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我展現這段時期學習成果的最佳時機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都陷入幻術了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八雲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八雲 是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 八雲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前進去的兩個人還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來八雲的能力漸漸覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去對付八雲跟紅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你待在這裡 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓援兵前來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個家紋是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是鞍馬一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕日紅 乖乖把八雲交出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們鞍馬一族對八雲有何企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的內部問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八雲是第三代委託給我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就休怪我無禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將計就計 讓我們反陷入幻術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 別急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些豆子也太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納命來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻術是奈何不了蟲子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你躲起來 味道卻消不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獸人分身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉剛力旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種半調子的幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對久經考驗的我們是無效的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放開我 快放開我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你一頭衝進敵人幻術裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師跟八雲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們四個都中了幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒她們的蹤影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到什麼了 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候對我施的幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 居然解不開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是繼我父親過世後執掌鞍馬一族的雲海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞍馬一族的雲海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 難怪不容易對付
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻術忍者 夕日紅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得到你的誇獎甚為榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你別做無謂的抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖把八雲交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你是夕日紅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了我的幻術又如何跟我鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會刺穿你的心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把八雲交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你傷害紅老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 難道你不長記性嗎 鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 敵人在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用幻術的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的分身可不是幻術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人連彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放棄八雲的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛讓八雲吃了點安神的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最好還是帶她回村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一個詳細的檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧有你幫忙 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 你也得趕緊接受治療
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾個傢伙一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他們暫時無法從幻術中清醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做了緊急處理 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過傷口很深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須趕緊回村才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八雲情緒不穩 反而讓我比較擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的同夥估計還會返回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護八雲的三個人沒了蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們和紅一起帶著八雲回村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再帶增援部隊前來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是幻術忍者 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應付得來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體可是久經鍛煉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:14:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會被鞍馬一族那種小幻術給蒙騙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為紅老師封印了你的幻術能力 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你懷恨在心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她打從心底裡討厭我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不希望我成為一名幻術忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誤會老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她這麼做一定有她的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才如果不是紅老師冒死營救你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要被人擄走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:15:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是鞍馬一族 我的族人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同族人為什麼要這麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙 你可以帶紅老師回村嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 自己能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師 請告訴我們真相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你不肯執教我們班有關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八雲所在的鞍馬一族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是以傲視群雄的幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佔據木葉重要地位的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但近年來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為培養不出上忍 中忍 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以家道中落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這時出現了一顆希望之星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是八雲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母和親戚都把希望寄托在宗家的獨生女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是從小身體虛弱的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法正式就讀忍者學校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負著雙親和族人希望的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入了絕望的深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不忍看我難過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是去找第三代火影大人求情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟叢雲交流後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代發現了八雲的優秀潛力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便打算交由我負責
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第三代火影大人的命令下 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師開始給我特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八雲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師她…紅老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許同為幻術忍者的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒八雲那種優秀的潛能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:18:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡不需要比我更厲害的幻術忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 老師怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種自私的人 怎麼配帶領你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對木葉而言 我也是眼中釘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師應該有所隱瞞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話 在回憶往事時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師的手顫抖不止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在講述動機時 手卻停止了顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個動機是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:19:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是謊言 心就不會動搖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她嫉妒八雲也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師應該是在為某人打掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師想掩護的人 比如…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師跟第三代火影大人的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣八雲短期內能力就不會覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水決堤溢出的時候早晚會來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞍馬一族的力量早晚會威脅到木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時 我們就不得不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的能力遭到封印
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對和第三代火影大人有關
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代是不可能下達這種命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟紅老師修煉沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一場突如其來的火災 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火勢迅速蔓延 根本無法救援
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父母都是上忍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能死於一場白天的火災呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事後 一方面告知這是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一方面卻把驗屍報告作為秘密封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非不是單純的火災
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母會死也是因為第三代的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 這決不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的話 紅老師的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰真誰假
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們都不像在騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有一件事我很確定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三代爺爺決不可能想除掉姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:22:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當務之急
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是帶老師她們回醫院治療…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.42,0:22:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:22:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻覺或真實 控制五感的人
